title: Fit Bar Fresh4you
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Organic, Western, Salad bar, Juice bar, Take-out, All Raw
description: The first Slovenian raw food centre, located in the Terme & Wellness LifeClass. Offers fruit and vegetable juices, fruit and green smoothies, vegan raw patisserie, raw salads, raw "meatballs" with seeds, and dehydrated crackers with selected spreads.
